# Group Users
This section groups the user resources.

# User [/api/users]
Collection of all Users of the platform.

+ Attributes
    + email: user@test.com (string, required) - must be valid email
    + firstName: John (string, required) - must be between 2 and 255 characters
    + lastName: Mark (string, required) - must be between 2 and 255 characters
    + phone: +1 650-253-0000 (string, optional) - must be between 2 and 45 characters

## Create a user [POST]

+ Attributes (User)

+ Request (application/json)
    Creates a new User.
    + Headers

                Authorization : Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJfaWQiOiI1NTY0YmRjNzA1NzUxNmFjMTMyZjkwMjAiLCJpYXQiOjE0MzI2NjU1NDMsImV4cCI6MTQzMzg3NTE0M30.SZli5UyiiWDmIu7YzduMdZ6317ws9q43clGSpr1GZII



    + Body

            {
                "email": "phillmont@rw.co",
                "firstName": "phill",
                "lastName": "beck",
                "phone": "+1 650-253-0000"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "user": {
                    "firstName": "phill",
                    "lastName": "beck",
                    "email": "phillmont@rw.co",
                    "phone": "+1 650-253-0000",
                    "roleId": 2,
                    "role": {}
                }
            }


