# Current User [/api/users/self]
The User that is currently authenticated with the API.

## Get Current User profile [GET]

+ Request (application/json)
    Used to retrieve the profile of the User currently authenticated with the API.

    + Headers

            Authorization : Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI1MzM1OGRhZDY0YzZiNWQ0MWFlMzA3MjgiLCJleHAiOjEzOTc0OTM0MTAsImlhdCI6MTM5NjI4MzgxMH0.LZD2THzehu7peh-nMVa6sFittsCN1hRqvzE4CMnYPRM

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
              "user": {
                  "id": 3,
                  "roleId": 2,
                  "email": "phillmont@rw.co",
                  "phone": null,
                  "firstName": "phill",
                  "lastName": "mont",
                  "status": "active",
                  "createdAt": "2016-04-11T14:12:23.276Z",
                  "updatedAt": "2016-04-11T14:12:23.276Z",
                  "role": {
                    "id": 2,
                    "name": "user"
                  }
              }
            }

